CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper August 5, 1961, pg. A15, reads: "FROGS' Teen Queen - Morris Fountain, chairman for the Frogs' teen-age dance, places a crown of flowers on the head of Marguerite Peters, center, who was named 'Queen' of the affair. Other lovely contestants are, left to right: Yvonne Rickmond, Rosalyn King. Marilyn Cobb, Gretel Cobb and Diana Fountain. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Three young men standing behind seven young women, including Marilyn Cobb and Gretel Cobb  in center, posed in Loendi Club for FROGS club teen dance with band in background
